{"tid":1739334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我知打仗時講呢啲，只係打飛機，但我真係好中意改變緊嘅香港。","createTime":"2019-11-19T14:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T14:40:05.000Z","uid":316098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1ba7483aefaf502bbb96e7d2df32bc17e7ca96","tid":1739334,"uid":316098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:19:14.000Z","msg":"今晚踎街食點心忽發奇想，香港會不會有這麼一天：<br />\n<br />\n文宣警告市民發泡膠有毒<br />\n罷食罷工用發泡膠外賣盒嘅餐廳<br />\n狂食環保餐廳<br />\n家長周圍派環保餐具<br />\n有環保餐具歌每個月遍地開花唱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WZ3kNtM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZ3kNtM.jpg&h=ab4b03ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔只發泡膠，<strong>其他大家本身懶得理嘅問題都一樣，同手解決、兄弟爬山</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n我知道香港有人等左呢種新社會模式好耐。<br />\n<br />\n話我知，你都肯，光復香港時候、以後，用手足力量，改變社會、環境、教會、經濟、重有當然嘅政治。<br />\n<br />\nsorryfor1999。我只係願香港光復之後，重光嘅香港人，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">知道我地be water嘅力量</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>再去建設一個美麗新香港</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港。"},{"pid":"d29d71e94304681301e77a88346aa23097117c48","tid":1739334,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"經歷咗5、6年醉生夢死，人心終於復甦"},{"pid":"c724f2bc4a7de49c5658e35ef5f475f20d0b48f3","tid":1739334,"uid":244152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1999<br />\n但支持"},{"pid":"c0c34c449433468e81f34ff8e7e814013707e02f","tid":1739334,"uid":316098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c724f2bc4a7de49c5658e35ef5f475f20d0b48f3","tid":1739334,"uid":244152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1999<br />\n但支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:40:05.000Z","msg":"sorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}